      "date": "2024-08-04 04:31:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe commit message looks good overall! However, here are some minor suggestions:\n\n* **Consistency:** While 'SPDX' is capitalized in the subject line, it's written as lowercase ('spdx') in the description. Choose one style and stick to it for consistency. Consider updating the description to also use 'SPDX'.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "1fd14cceb6de0d805d03f5c659c41d7c0ae4f4e7",
      "author": {
